  abstract={This paper gives a novel, context-aware approach to dynamically generate appropriate musical accompaniment for silent movies using transformer-based deep learning models. This project Building upon conventional methods the use of RNNs and CNNs, take a look at explores real-time processing, evaluating various techniques which include Vision Transformer for video evaluation and complicated song technology. The proposed framework consists of three levels: video analysis, song technology, and integration, with a focal point on maintaining temporal alignment. The assessment framework employs metrics like Detection Accuracy Rate and Synchronization Accuracy, at the identical time as additionally figuring out modern obstacles and suggesting future research directions, which include multimodal enhancement and personalization. This art work contributes to AI-pushed multimedia processing through supplying a strong method for context-conscious music embedding.},
